origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
{'name': 'MarineResourceAPI.analyze_data', 'description': 'This function analyzes the provided marine resource data and its impact on a specific real estate project.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'data', 'type': 'JSON', 'description': 'The marine resource data in JSON format, including fish species, coral reefs, and water quality.'}, {'name': 'projectID', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The unique identifier for the real estate project.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'analysis', 'description': 'The analysis of the marine resource data impact on the project.'}]}
请用以下格式进行回复:
想法: 你这一步的目标
动作: 你要调用的API名称
动作参数: JSON格式的参数输入,全部写在一行
调用工具 MarineResourceAPI.analyze_data, 它的参数输入如下: 'data'是'{"fish_species": 150, "coral_reefs": 200, "water_quality": "good"}', 'projectID'是'12345'.
